      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Is it really possible to teach yourself electric guitar?</p>
<p>People have been teaching themselves to play the electric guitar for years and more so than any other instrument, is is very common for most guitarists to be self taught.</p>
<p>Taking private lessons has always been a good idea but today with all of the multimedia courses available on the Internet it is very feasible to advance to quite a high level on your own. The video and audio examples if followed correctly will teach you the basics of guitar playing, show you the correct posture, how to hold your hands and which fingers to use etc.</p>
<p>Download a multimedia home study course and teach yourself electric guitar today.</p>
